text.section:
The permit shall give:
The name of the person performing the work;
The full extent of the work to be performed;
The name of the owner or owners of the property where the work is to be performed;
The location of the property where the work is to be performed, including county and street address; and
The master license number, if the work is required to be performed by a master heating, ventilation, and air conditioning contractor.
